            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            公务员拒绝加班，算不算违纪？          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      贝小拉                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                湖边看世界              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">湖边看世界</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">fo_gushi</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">湖边看世界，世界在湖边。聊聊体制内那些事，关注官场新生态。 关心官场就是关心自己。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.8342592592592593" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/U5fBOaXlIQm0DM3wAG6wKFKkvwiagpbjqFz6h8nVRz2fAQICbkmDuyfsAXtTHHN0RLE1oDbTC2klXFzzr9pyQpg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;"></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一些公务员拒绝加班，这算不算违纪呢？</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">这是一个很有争议的话题，不同的人有不同的看法。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">有些人认为，公务员是为国家和人民服务的，应该服从工作安排，不得无故拒绝加班。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">他们认为，公务员拒绝加班是不负责任的，是对职责和荣誉的背叛，是违反工作纪律和职业道德的行为。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">他们主张，对于这样的公务员，应该严肃处理，给予相应的处分或惩罚。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">另一些人则认为，公务员也是普通人，也有自己的生活和家庭。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">他们认为，公务员的工作时间应该按照法律规定，不应该随意延长或强制加班。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">他们认为，公务员拒绝加班是合理的，是维护自己的合法权益和健康的表现。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">他们主张，对于这样的公务员，应该尊重其选择，给予理解和支持。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">那么，究竟公务员拒绝加班，算不算违纪呢？</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这个问题没有一个简单的答案，需要根据具体的情况来分析和判断。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一方面，我们不能否认，公务员是国家机关的工作人员，承担着重要的社会责任和使命。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在一些特殊的时期或紧急的情况下，公务员需要加班或值班，以保证国家机关的正常运转和社会秩序的稳定。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-position: normal;text-wrap: wrap;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">根据《公务员法》第五十九条规定：公务员应当遵纪守法，不得有下列行为：</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-position: normal;text-wrap: wrap;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1、不担当，不作为，玩忽职守，贻误工作;</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-position: normal;text-wrap: wrap;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2、拒绝执行上级依法作出的决定和命令。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在特殊或紧急情况下，如果公务员无故拒绝加班或值班，就可能影响工作效率和质量，甚至造成严重的后果，就可能构成违纪行为。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">另一方面，我们也不能忽视，公务员也是人类社会的一员，享有基本的人权和尊严。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">根据我国《劳动法》等相关法律规定，工作时间一般不得超过每天八小时、每周四十四小时。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">如果需要延长工作时间或安排加班，则应该按照法律规定支付加班费或者安排补休。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">根据《</span><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">公务员法》第八十二条规定：“公务员在法定工作日之外加班的，应当给予相应的补休，不能补休的按照国家规定给予补助”。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">而且，在一些非紧急或非必要的情况下，强制公务员加班或值班，可能会损害其身心健康和家庭生活质量。</span><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">因此，在这种情况下，公务员拒绝加班或值班，并不构成违纪行为。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">应该说，拒绝加班是公务员的权利，但是需要有正当、合理的理由，尤其评估必要加班而不配合时，有可能被处以“不担当、不作为”的违纪处分。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">总之，我们既要尊重公务员的工作性质和职责要求，也要尊重公务员的个人权利和生活需求。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">只有这样，才能实现公务员队伍的健康发展和社会和谐。</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 82, 255);caret-color: var(--weui-BRAND);font-size: 17px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;"></span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1126584300" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
